---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Spotlight — Eugen Trapeznikov">
  <main style="flex:1;padding:40px 48px;overflow-y:auto;height:100vh;max-width:800px;">

    <a href="/" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:40px;transition:color .2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#E8601A'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--text3)'">← Back to work</a>

    <div style="margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:16px;">
        <span style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(232,96,26,0.08);color:#E8601A;border:0.5px solid rgba(232,96,26,0.2);">#sporttech</span>
        <span style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(232,96,26,0.08);color:#E8601A;border:0.5px solid rgba(232,96,26,0.2);">#media</span>
        <span style="fonze:11px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:rgba(232,96,26,0.08);color:#E8601A;border:0.5px solid rgba(232,96,26,0.2);">#edtech</span>
      </div>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:16px;">Spotlight —<br>Sports Bloggers Platform</h1>
      <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text2);max-width:560px;margin-bottom:28px;">Sports.ru is the largest sports media in the CIS. Spotlight was created as a free course to help people write about sports and grow into bloggers. The goal: attract more authors, raise content quality, increase UGS and session length.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:32px;padding:20px 0;border-top:0.5px solid var(--border);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;"><span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;cor:var(--text3);">Role</span><span style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);">Lead Product Designer</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;"><span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);">Company</span><span style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);">Sports.ru</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;"><span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);">Platform</span><span style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);">Web & Mobile</span></div>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;"><span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);">Year</span><span style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);">2024</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-label">01 — Intro</div>
      <div style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;">
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline style="width:100%;display:block;border-radius:12px;">
          <source src="https://framerusercontent.com/assets/m2BI9HEleHscvTEBP4oivYVHFV4.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Promo video featuring a well-known Sports.ru blogger</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-label">02 — Context & challenges</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Starting without a vision</h2>
      <p class="section-text">When I joined the project, the team had already spent two years preparing. The educational materials — lectures, tests, videos — were ready, but the design direction was still undefined. The main chwas that nobody had a clear vision of how the platform should look.</p>
      <p class="section-text">The situation was complicated by the fact that Sports.ru had just gone through a major rebranding. The company was still adjusting to its new identity, while the key visual developed earlier by an external studio didn't match the updated style at all. Users couldn't even recognize Spotlight as part of Sports.ru.</p>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:8px;">
        <div>
          <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/rQP3F6EJirUP4q0ac5655fpKQ4.png?width=800" alt="Key visual by external studio" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;" />
          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:24px;">Key visual by external studio</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/u0IE6jyEHUxes5Nhj0ALVHLWx40.png?width=800" alt="New company branding" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;" />
          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:24px;">New Sports.ru branding</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-label">03 — Process</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Structure first, visuals second</h2>
      <p class="section-text">We didn't have the luxury of time. Deadlines were strict, so I started with the essentials — mapping out the screens and creating wireframes. That gave us a solid structure we could later adapt to any visual concept.</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/VN59HFL7rdXyA9YCxrj6JF0bAQ.png?width=1600" alt="Screens map" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Screens map</p>

      <p class="section-text">At the same time, we held ongoing discussions with stakeholders and evelly aligned on a guiding principle: "Spotlight should feel different from Sports.ru, but still clearly connected to it." This gave us freedom beyond the constraints of the design system, while still allowing us to build on the new brand elements.</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/KMOEUhF1L4tiJtTBlG3KzvjBZ3w.png?width=1600" alt="First drafts" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">First drafts</p>

      <p class="section-text">From there, I experimented with different visual approaches and continuously gathered feedback from colleagues, authors, and users. Iteration by iteration, the picture became clearer. By the fifth design version, we had full stakeholder approval and encouraging feedback from our audience.</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/oXKAST5e3HkTmtmlpR8ofiYBI.png?width=1600" alt="One of the latest iterations" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">One of the latest iterations</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-label">04 — Design decisions</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Simplicity and engagement</h2>
      <p class="section-text">The homepage featured a promo video starring a well-known actor who was also one of our bloggers — an instantly familiar and trustworthy face for the community.</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/J1yCoSSHqIAlENGVzxlVDfdtw8.png?width=1600" alt="Homepage" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Homepage design</p>

      <p class="section-text">The course program was designed to give users a sense of scope at a glance: on desktop, all lessons were visible in one screen, while on mobile I worked to mize unnecessary scrolling.</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/uBbyP77vIAkpZJe5KGLIeGphwbc.png?width=1600" alt="Course program" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Course program — desktop & mobile</p>

      <p class="section-text">Lesson pages were centered around video content, with assignments and additional materials placed right below. Even small details, like the "join the Telegram channel" block, were designed to appear and disappear at the right moment.</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/gWghJSoNODHh0RW1qFJFV2cqi0.png?width=1600" alt="Lesson page" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Lesson page</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/JVToiz7AQ5Tj9nPvBtCsWiXjk.png?width=1600" alt="Finalesign" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Final design — block priorities in layout</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/s9C7assajXLOj4mIYpzzQCyqdmM.png?width=1600" alt="Mobile view" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Mobile — all key blocks in first view</p>

      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/ISvntJyoghZE8ooGSQhap4i9Ek.png?width=1600" alt="Final screens" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;">Final screens</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-label">05 — Outcome</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Results</h2>
      <p class="section-text">A clear, visuallging, and mobile-friendly platform that empowered new voices in sports media and strengthened the Sports.ru blogging community. The product is actively developing and continues to attract new authors.</p>
      <img src="https://framerusercontent.com/images/ZekEckxI7rbtXcogAHxTQCjh6V8.png?width=1600" alt="Results" style="width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;margin-bottom:8px;" />
    </div>

    <a href="/cases/yollet" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 24px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--bg2);border:0.5px solid var(--border);text-decoration:none;margin-top:64px;transition:border-color .2s;" class="next-case">
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:4px;">Next case</div>
        <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);">Yollet — Crypto Wallet</div>
      </div>
      <span style="font-size:20px;color:var-text3);">→</span>
    </a>

  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .section-label { font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px; }
  .section-label::after { content:'';flex:1;height:0.5px;background:var(--border); }
  .section-title { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:12px; }
  .section-text { font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:20px; }
  .next-case:hover { border-color: rgba(232,96,26,0.35) !important; }
</style>
